HLS 26RS-1313 ORIGINAL
HB NO. 583
Proposed law changes present law to require a registering entity to offer or accept a request
for security registration in beneficiary form.
Present law provides that if a registration in beneficiary form is offered by a registering
entity, the owner requesting the registration in beneficiary form assents to the protections
given to the registering entity.
Proposed law changes present law and removes the language related to the registering entity
offering request a security registration in beneficiary form.
(Amends R.S. 9:1711.6(A))
